import {createSlice} from '@reduxjs/toolkit'

const initialState = [
    {
        id: "1",
        title: "Do something",
        categoryId: 2,
        category: "Work",
        createdDate: "05-05-2022 12:40:00",
        deadlineDate: "5/29/2022 12:40:00 PM",
        isDone: false,
        doneDate: ""
    },
    {
        id: "2",
        title: "Do something 2",
        categoryId: 1,
        category: "Uncategorized",
        createdDate: "10-05-2022 12:40:00",
        deadlineDate: "5/30/2022 12:40:00 PM",
        isDone: false,
        doneDate: ""
    },

    {
        id: "3",
        title: "Do something 3",
        categoryId: 3,
        category: "School",
        createdDate: "09-05-2022 12:40:00",
        deadlineDate: "5/29/2022 17:40:00 PM",
        isDone: false,
        doneDate: ""
    },
]

const toDoTasksSlice = createSlice({
    name: 'toDoTasks',
    initialState,
    reducers: {}
})

export default toDoTasksSlice.reducer
